Class Relation

  • java.lang.Object
    • fuzzydl.Relation

  • public class Relation
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a role assertion of the form (object individual, role, lower bound for the degree) with respect to a subject individual.
    Author:
    Fernando Bobillo
